### Register new user account
POST http://localhost:4421/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Password123!"
}

